name: An Angel Called Death
description:
Azrael resides in the Third Heaven. It
presents itself to souls in powerful
metaphors as the archangel of death
himself, while the common man
meets lesser angels. Prophets are
invited courteously by it, and saints
are said to meet it in beautiful and
wondrous forms. 2400 x 3000 pixels.
Original Music by parrott_ism
